event: I would advise my younger self not to go out of my way to impress people, as those who like me will do so regardless.
I sometimes feel lazy and wish I had a better work ethic.
Last night, I felt really happy while hanging out with my friends, sharing stories, and laughing.
My grandmother was a positive influence on me from a young age because of her strong and powerful character.
The hardest decision I ever made was deciding whether or not to divorce my husband because we weren't getting along.
I am close with my grandparents because they raised me, unlike my parents who weren't really in the picture.
When my sister died, it was really traumatizing for me.
I feel guilty about not talking to my grandparents as much as I should.
